                              reviewText:
                                   "St. Joseph Cathedral - A Charming Piece of History in Hanoi!\n\nHey folks, if you're in Hanoi, make sure to swing by St. Joseph Cathedral! This place is a real gem. The stunning French Gothic architecture will make you go \"wow.\" I mean, those towering spires and intricate stained glass windows are something else! Step inside, and you'll feel the peaceful vibes, away from the hustle and bustle of the city. Whether you're religious or not, it's a perfect spot to take a moment of serenity. Just keep in mind, it can get crowded with tourists, so timing is key. Add a visit to St. Joseph Cathedral to your Hanoi itinerary—you won't be disappointed!",
