                                   "Super fun experience for our first night in Hanoi! Affordable tickets which you can purchase on the night at the book or with a ticketing agency like we did.\n\nThe atmosphere of the theatre was cozy and small but nevertheless impressive. The show was spectacular with beautiful traditional cultural music that encompassed live instruments and singing.\n\nThe puppet show was amusing, entertaining and very impressive. For a short one hour show it's definitely worth visiting and watching as a means of embracing the culture and supporting the years old artistic tradition.",
