                              reviewText:
                                   "The Temple of Literature,\nVietnam's first university holds a special place in every Vietnamese heart. 🇻🇳📚\nWith its grand architecture and ancient engineering, this place is a visual delight. Inside, you'll find rare literature articles preserved beautifully.\nMultiple well-maintained courtyards offer endless photo opportunities. Every corner here is extraordinary and captivating! 😍📸",
