                              reviewText:
                                   "The interior design of the is not too crowded, the temperature is comfortable and the appearance of the museum is impressive. The presentation of exhibition is quite traditional. However, the the caption of the some artifacts are too simple.\n\nBesides, the offical website shows that it needs to have extra tickets for taking photos, but the staff said that no extra fee for phototaking. The information in the website is not updated.",
