                              reviewText:
                                   "Very informative, but the first building could use some more maintenance. There are two buildings across the streets. The first building shows ancient Vietnam to pre French colonial time. The second building shows Vietnam during the French colonisation to modern day Vietnam. We recommend spending more time in the second building since it has a lot more information.\n\nStudent discount is available.",
