                              reviewerName: "Dale Van Aarde",
                              reviewText:
                                   "What an amazing and insightful experience.\n\nThe mesuem itself is filled with so many natural elements of history from the history of man to the history of the important families of Vietnam. The struggles they went through were just insane.\n\nThe items in the museum have been looked after and are in such great condition. Just loved the old school cupboards with the mother of pearls. The mesuem also offers audio files for each of the pieces so make sure to take some headphones to listen.\n\nThe meusem area is very large and open. It is both child friendly as well as caiters for people with disabilities.\n\nI would highly recommend visiting the natural History museum.",
