                              reviewerName: "Quynh Anh Nguyen",
                              reviewText:
                                   "I regret having to write this review for a restaurant which has, in the past, been one of my go-tos for when friends and family come to visit Hanoi.\n\nThe quality of service at this restaurant has declined significantly, to the point where the staff actively ignore customers and behave incredibly rudely to them.\n\nBefore I ordered, I and my partner overheard a customer arguing with the staff about how long it took to get the bill. At the time, overhearing this, we assumed that the customer was being unreasonable. However, we later realized that the service at the restaurant was terrible.\n\nDuring the meal, the service was so so. A few things on the menu were missing and they brought us the wrong items from the menu. Not a big deal. However, when we had finished eating, I asked for the bill. All three waiters were on their phones and two of them had their headphones in. One of them acknowledged me, so I decided to wait. 5 minutes passed and he still hadn't moved, so I asked for the bill again. He again nodded to me, showing that he heard me, but he still didn't move and continued to play games on his phone. At this point, two members of staff were sitting opposite each other, playing games on their phones and drinking milk tea. Finally, after almost 15m of waiting (the restaurant was not at all busy) I decided to go to the counter and just wait there until I got the bill. When I got there, a different staff member came out from the kitchen and served me. The waiter who I had previously asked the bill from was still sitting there playing on his phone. I told him that the level of service was really unprofessional and he didn't even look at me, he simply mumbled something under his breath. I then paid and left.\n\nI have been to this restaurant maybe 10 times over 4 years and will never go back. Because I really like the food and decor of the place, I tried to be patient with the staff and to be understanding. However, I cannot believe the level of contempt that the staff treat the customers with and I will never go back to this place again. A real shame as I have previously been such a fan.",
