                                   "Great hotel with perfect location in the heart of old quarter.\nStaff are very nice and thoughtful.\nRooms are very nice and clean.\nBed is so comfy and pillow is nice and thick.\nGym is basic but you can do enough in there.\nThe only bag thing was there was no chairs or high desk. If you need to work or sit at a computer, your back will have a hard time.",
