                              reviewText:
                                   "Located in the center of Old Quarter, Hanoi. This made us very easy for us to commute to local attractions. 10 minute walk away to Train street and market. Surrounded by many coffee shops and massage centers. Easy access to bike rentals and the staff was always ready to help at any hour of the day, night shift boys were super friendly and accommodating. Linda, the manager responded to us very well and helped us in booking tours and cabs. Rooms are good and spacious. I would surely recommend this hotel.",
