                              reviewerName: "Stadt Freiburg",
                              reviewText:
                                   "The best hotel on our trip! The staff is so friendly and dedicated that you would think they were all the owners of the hotel.\nEven before we arrived in Hannoi, the travel manager (Linda) sent us an email with tips and warnings for our trip through Vietnam. She then helped us perfectly to plan our next trip. Even when we had already traveled further, she was a trustworthy contact for us during our further trip and organized many things for us.\nThe hotel is super clean and every wish is fulfilled immediately. All the employees gave us good tips about what was worth seeing and what wasn't really worth it.\nThere is no large breakfast buffet like in other hotels, because you order à la carte and the food is freshly and individually prepared for each guest.\nWhen we had to leave very early, the staff started extra early to prepare breakfast for us. We felt very comfortable in this family atmosphere and are therefore happy to recommend this hotel.",
                              rating: 5,
