                              reviewerName: "Pietro Caneo",
                              reviewText:
                                   "Linda, Saffron, and the rest of the staff were so amazing! I stayed with my family here during their first visit to Asia, and could not have asked for a better place to welcome us into Hanoi. The staff was attentive, friendly, and warm from the get go - even before we arrived. We were welcome with tea, and a long list of recommendations for what to do while in Hanoi. Top notch level of service, and perfect location - cannot ask for anything else from a hotel! Will definitely be back",
