                              time: "2024-06-16T09:51:29.000Z",
                              reviewerName: "Bethany Donnelly",
                              reviewText:
                                   "After staying here for around a week I cannot recommend this hotel enough for anyone wanting accommodation in Hanoi. It is a lovely hotel situated in the heart of the city, the rooms are clean and modern and the hotel also offers free breakfast everyday, with western options and the rooms are also cleaned daily. However, what sets this hotel apart is the team that work here with a massive special mentioned to Chloe and Linda. The hotel staff will be able to assist you with either any enquiries or problems you have. On my trip I had a little disaster and I had to unexpectedly return to Hanoi and I checked straight back into the hotel to be greeted with a big smile from the whole team and they were amazing with helping me sort everything I needed to. They went above and beyond, more than I could ever imagine and I couldn’t be more grateful for the team here as I’m not sure what I would of done without them. Once again I could recommend this hotel enough, if you are looking for a nice, lovely hotel with the most welcoming and attentive staff then stay here.\n\nThank you so much team! Love Beth and Meg",
