                              reviewerName: "Maria jose Hidalgo",
                              reviewText:
                                   "Exceptionally friendly staff with excellent English, making communication a breeze.\n\nThey were kind enough to store our luggage, and the rooms were impeccably clean.\n\nWe ended up choosing this hotel as a last-minute option due to mixed reviews elsewhere. It turned out to be a fantastic stay. However, the only downside was the steep price tag.\n\nWe got a balcony too with a great view",
                              rating: 4,
