                              reviewerName: "Kushal Agrawal",
                              reviewText:
                                   "If you want to experience hospitality at its best standards then stay at this hotel. Mrs. Linda (Manager), Chloe, Trang, Duong, Nhi, and the Cleaning Staff leave no stone unturned to make you feel welcomed. Mrs. Linda gave me all the information and booked me a professional city tour guide. When I found some ants in my room, she upgraded me to a better room. Doung is a great chef, he made food as per my requests. He also serves in room and helps as a bellboy. Chloe is always dressed traditionally, which is a delight to watch. She served me in restaurant and helped me at reception. Trang in the evening shift helped me to book food from outside. She also made it warm and served in the restaurant. Nhi is the youngest, she dresses modern, and serves in the restaurant. They don't expect any extra money, but rather give you discounts on their services. They also booked me an Airport taxi. After staying in 100's of hotels around the world, I feel they are better than most 5 star hotels in terms of their hospitality.",
