                              reviewText:
                                   "Linda and Chloe (and other staff) were very friendly and helpful. Linda helped me threw whatsapp communication to book ha long bay and ninh binh tour and airport transport. I really recommend them both tours.\n\nI asked for a quiet room and they gave me free upgrade to give me the family room on the highest floor for less sound noise. Their location is very good in the old quarter of Hanoi.\n\nBreakfast is to order and I liked the congee and fruit.\n\nIt's a small and cozy hotel, I recommend it.\n\nI still recommend to bring ear plugs with you.",
