                              reviewerName: "Ferhat Uddin",
                              reviewText:
                                   "Linda and the team were wonderful, and they went above and beyond for us - organising tours, transfer, restaurant bookings, even flowers and cake for my sister in laws birthday! They were always warm and smiley and made our stay very special, thank you! Rooms are lovely, modern, and clean.",
