                                   "The Long Bien Bridge would have been just another bridge to me, if it weren't for the motorbike city tour guide who drove us here one evening and told us the features and history of the bridge in such an engaging manner. Now, with greater admiration for this bridge, I made sure to get a postcard with this bridge in it! 😊",
