                              reviewText:
                                   "I imagine if it was open it would be beautiful but looks quite similar to other structures in the area. There is no way inside and the location on maps is wrong. large groups of people taking photos outside. Market people and bike riders/taxi stand outside and are quite aggressive to tourists walking past that you take their services. Overall a let down 👎",
